        </div>

        <div class="home-resource-grid">
            <article class="home-resource-card">
                <span class="home-resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false">
                        <path d="M7 3h7.59A2 2 0 0 1 16 3.59l3.41 3.41A2 2 0 0 1 20 8.41V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Zm7 1.5V8h3.5Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div class="home-resource-content">
                    <strong>Manual de uso</strong>
                    <span>Instrucciones claras para conocer el funcionamiento general del sistema y sus modulos principales.</span>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="home-resource-card">
                <span class="home-resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false">
                        <path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4v18H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2Zm8-2h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-6Zm1.5 4v2h4V7Zm0 4v2h4v-2Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div class="home-resource-content">
                    <strong>Guias</strong>
                    <span>Recorridos practicos paso a paso para tareas frecuentes, procesos internos y buenas practicas de uso.</span>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="home-resource-card">
                <span class="home-resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false">
                        <path d="M12 2 2 7l10 5 8.18-4.09V17H22V7ZM6 11.91V16l6 3 6-3v-4.09l-6 3Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div class="home-resource-content">
                    <strong>Documentacion</strong>
                    <span>Espacio pensado para reunir politicas, novedades, referencias operativas y contenido institucional.</span>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div class="home-coming-soon">
            <div class="home-coming-soon-copy">
                <span class="home-coming-soon-kicker">Proximamente</span>
                <h3>Estamos preparando una base de conocimiento para Nexa</h3>
                <p>
                    Aqui se publicaran tutoriales, preguntas frecuentes, actualizaciones del sistema y material de consulta
                    para que cada usuario tenga apoyo rapido en su trabajo diario.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@section Scripts {
    <script>
        (() => {
            const timeElement = document.getElementById("home-current-time");
            const dateElement = document.getElementById("home-current-date");

            if (!timeElement || !dateElement) {
                return;
            }

            const timeFormatter = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("es-CO", {
                timeZone: "America/Bogota",
                hour: "2-digit",
                minute: "2-digit",
                second: "2-digit",
                hour12: true
            });

            const dateFormatter = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("es-CO", {
                timeZone: "America/Bogota",
                weekday: "long",
                day: "2-digit",
                month: "long",
                year: "numeric"
            });

            const capitalize = (value) => value.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + value.slice(1);

            const updateClock = () => {
                const now = new Date();
                timeElement.textContent = timeFormatter.format(now);
                dateElement.textContent = capitalize(dateFormatter.format(now));
            };

            updateClock();
            window.setInterval(updateClock, 1000);
        })();
    </script>
}
